    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require hospitality venues to show the content of any sugar added to food items",
        "additional_details": "Simply impose the obligation to indicate the amount of added sugar on the menu, under pain of criminal and civil liability.",
        "background": "People have a right to know, for their own health, when products served in restaurants or fast food have added sugar. This will better allow people to avoid health risks associated with excessive consumption of artificially produced sugar.",
